                The material displayed on the Website is provided without any
                guarantees, conditions, or warranties as to its accuracy. To the
                extent permitted by law, we exclude:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-6 mt-2 text-sm font-light">
                <li>
                    All conditions, warranties, and other terms which might
