                and we have the right to use, copy, distribute, and disclose to third
                parties any such material.
            </p>

            <h2 class="font-normal text-base tracking-widest mt-10">
                8. ACCEPTABLE USE
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 font-light tracking-wider text-sm">
                These content standards apply to all material you contribute to
                the Website. Contributions must comply with the law and must
                not:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-12 text-sm font-light mt-2">
                <li>
                    Contain defamatory, obscene, offensive, or hateful material;
                </li>
                <li>Promote sexually explicit material or violence;</li>
                <li>
                    Infringe any copyright, database right, or trademark of any
                    other person;
                </li>
                <li>Be likely to deceive any person;</li>
                <li>Promote illegal activity;</li>
                <li>Be threatening, abusive, or invade another's privacy;</li>
                <li>Be used to impersonate any person;</li>
                <li>Advocate or promote any unlawful act.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="font-normal text-base tracking-widest mt-10">
                9. VIRUSES, HACKING AND OTHER OFFENSES
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 font-light tracking-wider text-sm">
                You must not misuse the Website by knowingly introducing viruses
