            </p>

            <h2 class="font-normal text-base tracking-widest mt-10">
                10. LINKING TO OUR WEBSITE
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 font-light tracking-wider text-sm">
                You must not link to our homepage without permission. We reserve
                the right to withdraw linking permission without notice.
            </p>

            <h2 class="font-normal text-base tracking-widest mt-10">
                11. LINKS FROM OUR WEBSITE
